---
output: svg
---
@startuml
set namespaceSeparator none
skinparam wrap_width 150

left to right direction

actor User

User --> (1. select template)
User --> (2. write uml diagram)

note right of User
{{
    skinparam wrap_width 150
    start

    while (count < max?)
      :count = count + increment;
    endwhile

    stop
}}
end note

@enduml
